data.description: Welcome to 2018 Clara Lake Court, a charming one-story haven in the heart of Waterside Estates! This meticulously maintained move-in-ready home has 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths plus a home office/dining area. The property has been freshly painted inside and out, with newly carpeted bedrooms and upgraded LVT wood-like flooring. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac, this residence offers tranquility, complete with a backyard shed for extra storage. Enjoy the Waterside Estates lifestyle, centered around a serene lake with a paved walking trail, a community pool, parks, lakeside pavilion, plus pickleball and tennis courts. Convenience meets comfort with a prime location off 99/Grand Parkway, surrounded by restaurants, shopping, great schools, entertainment, and much more! Don't miss out on this gem with excellent FBISD schools. Make sure to see the Upgrades in Documents. Schedule your showing today!
